data.description: This is a Southern Maryland Debutante! Don't miss this gorgeous must see single family home in the Bryans Crossing neighborhood of Bryans Road, Maryland.  Previously the model home, this beauty is equipped with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths and a fully finished lower level. Perfect for Entertaining. Open floorplan with high ceilings and lots of windows. Granite CounterTops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Hardwood Floors, Fireplace, Spacious Family Room & Owner's Suite w/Sitting Room and Tray Ceiling, Separate Vanities, Walk-In Closets, and Two Car Garage, let's just say it has all the bells and whistles!
